he key to solving the crime lies not in where you look for truth, but how you look. From the windswept sand dunes of the coastline to the badlands of the hinterland, Y Gwyll is a series of stories that are original and local, yet timeless and universal.</p>","updated":1612710647,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1778"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1014625"}}},{"id":1779,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1779/remedy","name":"Remedy","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2014-02-24","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":[]},"rating":{"average":7.9},"weight":0,"network":{"id":67,"name":"Global","country":{"name":"Canada","code":"CA","timezone":"America/Halifax"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":40329,"thetvdb":277631,"imdb":"tt3182934"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/10/25284.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/25284.jpg"},"summary":"<p>A unique, high-stakes medical drama that goes beyond the operating room and the ER, to reveal a compelling community of hospital staff who make the healing happen. The series follows Griffin Conners, son of the Chief of Staff, brother to both a surgeon and a nurse, and now – medical school dropout. Having been kicked out in a haze of disgrace, Griffin is forced to return to Broadview Hospital as its newest orderly, where he gets a new perspective on a world he thought he knew through a colorful cast of cleaners, project aides, transport workers and more.</p>","updated":1573151179,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1779"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155381"}}},{"id":1780,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1780/finding-carter","name":"Finding Carter","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Family"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premi