cars at traffic lights. The truck sparks reactions wherever it goes, from Manhattan to the Bronx - plus on road trips to New Jersey, Maryland, DC, Chicago, and beyond. When clients climb aboard, they are often seeking answers to burning questions they have kept buried deep inside of them - sometimes for decades. They reveal the doubts that keep them awake at night, and ask for Jared's help in putting an end to their most personal mysteries. From astonishing stories like \"I think I was kidnapped at birth and have found my mother\" and \"I think the man I'm dating might be my brother,\" to personal revelations such as \"I may have found my sperm donor father,\" to touching stories like \"I think I have a twin sister\" there are no limits to the variety of questions people have about their DNA - right in the middle of traffic.</p>","updated":1514287366,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1781"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/177963"}}},{"id":1782,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1782/500-questions","name":"500 Questions","type":"Game Show","language":"English","genres":["Family"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-20","officialSite":"http://abc.go.com/shows/500-questions","schedule":{"time":"20:00","days":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":3,"name":"ABC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":45190,"thetvdb":295573,"imdb":"tt4591316"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/64/161105.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/64/161105.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Hosted by Dan Harris, <b>500 Questions</b> challenges the smartest people in the country to achieve the seemingly impossible task of answering 500 of the most difficult general knowledge questions ever devised. There'