aximum eight lifeguards on duty at any one time, and over 40,000 beachgoers on a summer's day, the question arises 'is everything they've got enough'? Performing around 2,500 rescues each season and with crowds exceeding 2.5 million people per year, the team certainly has their work cut out for them. The tight knit group work and play together, keeping each other in check and their feet planted firmly on the ground. Experience the action through the eyes of lifeguards as they deal with everything from shark scares to mass rescues, resuscitations, lost children and thieves.</p><p>Bondi Rescue celebrates the unsung heroes of Australia's best asset - the beach.</p>","updated":1618798504,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1815"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2073564"}}},{"id":1816,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1816/flipping-ships","name":"Flipping Ships","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-04-24","officialSite":"http://www.animalplanet.com/tv-shows/flipping-ships/","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Friday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":92,"name":"Animal Planet","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48664,"thetvdb":294906,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/302/755283.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/302/755283.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Flipping Ships </b>follows McCain and his Boats Have Souls business in a six-part series. In each episode, this quirky band of gear heads perform acts of nautical salvation on boats that have been abandoned for so long, they're beginning to forge with nature ... and not in a good way! When boat's floorboards have long been replaced by grass and dirt, the team goes to work reinventing these disasters into fishing vessels, open water cruisers and family houseboats.</p>","updated":1617545318,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1816"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/165631"}}},{"id":1817,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1817/the-truth-about-cats","name":"The Truth About Cats","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-04-24","officialSite":"http://channel.nationalgeographic.com/wild/the-truth-about-cats/","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Friday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":83,"name":"National Geographic WILD","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48659,"thetvdb":null,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/12/31637.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/12/31637.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Making use of the latest technology, militarygrade GPS trackers, x-rays, cat-cams and specialized photography, <b>The Truth About Cats</b> explores how a cat learns to function as a wild animal in a domestic world; the extraordinary ways in which cats are able to use their senses to interpret their environment; and the remarkable feline skill of inter-species communication and co-operation.</p>","updated":1586490595,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1817"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155192"}}},{"id":1818,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1818/i-can-do-that","name":"I Can Do That","type":"Variety","language":"English","genres":["Comedy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-26","officialSite":"http://www.nbc.com/i-can-do-that","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":1,"name":"NBC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48672,"thetvdb":294854,"imdb":"tt4723892"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/121/304635.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/121/304635.jpg"},"summary":"<p>NBC puts six celebrities to the test in its new one-hour comedy variety series, <b>I Can Do That</b>.<br /><br />Comedian-actor-producer Marlon Wayans (\"Scary Movie\" franchise) serves as host. Six of America's brightest entertainers come together to compete and showcase their talents with breathtaking and unique acts - featuring skills they did not even know they had.</p><p>Joining Wayans for this summer series will be acclaimed dancer and choreographer Cheryl Burke (\"Dancing with the Stars\"), superstar recording artists Ciara, Joe Jonas and Nicole Scherzinger, national stand-up comedian Jeff Dye (\"Last Comic Standing\") and actor Alan Ritchson (\"The Wedding Ringer\").</p><p>Each week, in front of a live audience, the six cast members will enter a friendly rivalry as they choose their favorite act - what they think they can master - and who they would like to pair up with to master that act. The acts will span every variety of entertainment from song and dance to magic and danger. They will also feature some of America's biggest-name performers in guest-starring roles.</p><p>With their acts selected, the duos make their way into the training studio, where they work with their expert coach for five days to produce an amazing act to perform on the next week's show. After a week of intensive training, the celebrities return to the stage to perform their act in hopes of scoring the top slot on the night's scoreboard.</p><p>With no judges or eliminations, <i>I Can Do That</i> allows the cast to show off their untapped talents and enjoy a little friendly competition along the way. After six weeks of exploring their own unique talent range, one cast member will be revealed as the season's ultimate entertainer.</p>","updated":1612607115,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1818"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155220"}}},{"id":1819,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1819/dark-matter","name":"Dark Matter","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Action","Adventure","Science-Fiction"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-12","officialSite":"http://www.space.ca/show/dark-matter/","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Friday"]},"rating":{"average":8.4},"weight":92,"network":{"id":7,"name":"CTV Sci-Fi Channel","country":{"name":"Canada","code":"CA","timezone":"America/Halifax"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47282,"thetvdb":292174,"imdb":"tt4159076"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/122/305066.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/122/305066.jpg"},"summary":"<p>In <b>Dark Matter</b>, the crew of a derelict spaceship is awakened from stasis with no memories of who they are or how they got on board. Facing threats at every turn, they have to work together to survive a voyage charged with vengeance, betrayal and hidden secrets.</p>","updated":1586781571,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1819"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1170577"}}},{"id":1820,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1820/proof","name":"Proof","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Supernatural"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-16","officialSite":"http://www.tntdrama.com/shows/proof.html","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":7.3},"weight":8,"network":{"id":14,"name":"TNT","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":36943,"thetvdb":281708,"imdb":"tt3595806"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/29511.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/29511.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Jennifer Beals plays Dr. Carolyn Tyler, who has suffered the recent, devastating loss of her teenage son, the breakup of her marriage and a growing estrangement from her daughter. Carolyn is persuaded by Ivan Turing (Modine), a cancer-stricken tech inventor and billionaire to investigate cases of reincarnation, near-death experiences, hauntings and other phenomena, all of it in the search for evidence that death is not the end.</p>","updated":1574299341,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1820"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155229"}}},{"id":1821,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1821/ballers","name":"Ballers","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Comedy","Sports"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-06-21","officialSite":"http://www.hbo.com/ballers","schedule":{"time":"22:30","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.6},"weight":87,"network":{"id":8,"name":"HBO","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":38517,"thetvdb":281714,"imdb":"tt2891574"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/207/519929.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/207/519929.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Looking at the lives of former and current football players, <b>Ballers</b> follows former superstar Spencer Strasmore as he gets his life on track in retirement while mentoring other current and former players through the daily grind of the business of football.</p>","updated":1575902654,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1821"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1696276"}}},{"id":1822,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1822/the-brink","name":"The Brink","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Comedy","War"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-06-21","officialSite":"http://www.hbo.com/the-brink","schedule":{"time":"22:30","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.7},"weight":8,"network":{"id":8,"name":"HBO","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":37973,"thetvdb":278469,"imdb":"tt3216586"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/29606.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/29606.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>The Brink</b> focuses on a geopolitical crisis and its effect on three disparate and desperate men: Walter Larson, the US Secretary of State; Alex Talbot, a lowly Foreign Service officer; and Zeke Tilson, an ace Navy fighter pilot. These three compromised souls must pull through the chaos around them to save the planet from World War Three.</p>","updated":1584549205,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1822"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/185640"}}},{"id":1823,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1823/between","name":"Between","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Science-Fiction","Mystery"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-21","officialSite":"https://www.netflix.com/title/80022632","schedule":{"time":"","days":[]},"rating":{"average":6.7},"weight":53,"network":null,"webChannel":{"id":1,"name":"Netflix","country":null},"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47159,"thetvdb":293194,"imdb":"tt4132692"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/61/153690.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/61/153690.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Between </b>is the story of a town under siege from a mysterious disease that has wiped out everybody except those 21 years old and under. The series explores the power vacuum that results when a government has quarantined a 10-mile diameter area and left the inhabitants to fend for themselves.</p>","updated":1605702696,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1823"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/808429"}}},{"id":1824,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1824/fear-the-walking-dead","name":"Fear the Walking Dead","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Action","Horror"],"status":"Running","runtime":60,"averageRuntime":62,"premiered":"2015-08-23","officialSite":"http://www.amc.com/shows/fear-the-walking-dead","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.8},"weight":100,"network":{"id":20,"name":"AMC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48384,"thetvdb":290853,"imdb":"tt3743822"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/299/748757.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/299/748757.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Living in the same universe as <i>The Walking Dead</i>, <b>Fear the Walking Dead </b>is a gritty drama that explores the onset of the undead apocalypse through the lens of a fractured family. Set in a city where people come to escape, shield secrets, and bury their pasts, a mysterious outbreak threatens to disrupt what little stability high school guidance counselor Madison Clark and English teacher Travis Manawa have managed to assemble. The everyday pressure of blending two families while dealing with resentful, escapist, and strung out children takes a back seat when society begins to break down. A forced evolution, a necessary survival of the fittest takes hold, and our dysfunctional family must either reinvent themselves or embrace their darker histories.</p>","updated":1620930696,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1824"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2044876"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2044879"}}},{"id":1825,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1825/the-expanse","name":"The Expanse","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Science-Fiction","Thriller","Mystery"],"status":"Running","runtime":null,"averageRuntime":56,"premiered":"2015-12-14","officialSite":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07YL9WK1S/","schedule":{"time":"","days":["Wednesday"]},"rating":{"average":8.8},"weight":99,"network":null,"webChannel":{"id":3,"name":"Amazon Prime Video","country":null},"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":41967,"thetvdb":280619,"imdb":"tt3230854"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/283/709553.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/283/709553.jpg"},"summary":"<p>A thriller set two hundred years in the future, <b>The Expanse</b> follows the case of a missing young woman who brings a hardened detective and a rogue ship's captain together in a race across the solar system to expose the greatest conspiracy in human history.</p>","updated":1619502927,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1825"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1945908"}}},{"id":1827,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1827/black-work","name":"Black Work","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Thriller"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-21","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.6},"weight":8,"network":{"id":35,"name":"ITV","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":44712,"thetvdb":296402,"imdb":"tt3959576"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/12/31205.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/12/31205.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Black Work</b> is the story of Jo Gillespie, a woman who's husband is shot dead in the line of action, in his job as a undercover cop. Jo, a police officer herself soon has to confront issues in her marriage and family life in order to discover who really killed her husband.</p>","updated":1574299324,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1827"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/181916"}}},{"id":1828,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1828/wentworth","name":"Wentworth","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime"],"status":"Running","runtime":60,"premiered":"2013-05-01","officialSite":"https://www.showcasechannel.com.au/shows/wentworth/","schedule":{"time":"20:30","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":8.4},"weight":94,"network":{"id":270,"name":"Showcase","country":{"name":"Australia","code":"AU","timezone":"Australia/Sydney"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":33365,"thetvdb":264234,"imdb":"tt2433738"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/158/396176.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/158/396176.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Fans of the iconic Prisoner Cell Block H series, which pushed boundaries over three decades ago and still boasts a loyal following worldwide today, will remember Bea Smith as gutsy and fearless, ruling Wentworth Correctional Centre with an iron fist. But who was Bea Smith before prison? How did a wife and mother from the suburbs become a top dog without rival? Wentworth Prison is a dynamic, often confronting, drama series that begins with Bea's early days in prison. Set in the present day, it is a modern adaptation of Prisoner Cell Block H that contemporises legendary characters and their stories for today's audience.</p><p>This series takes the viewer inside to an uncompromising environment that explores the politics of women in a world without men, and how such a threatening experience both challenges and often changes those confined and working behind the razor wire. The audience will be introduced to Bea all over again and meet her allies and enemies in the form of iconic inmates: Doreen Anderson, Liz Birdsworth and Franky Doyle, and there are new faces such as Jacs Holt, the ruthless matriarch of a crime family who now reigns over Wentworth. Favourite offices will also return. Meg Jackson carries a shameful secret; Vera Bennett, the well-meaning officer who discovers everyone has a price; Erica Davidson, the crusading Lawyer and Matthew Fletcher who believes in retribution rather than rehabilitation. And a new face, Meg's husband Will Jackson, whose past still haunts him.</p><p>Each episode explores an individual character's back story, providing an insight to what makes them tick and the circumstances that led them to Wentworth. In doing so we discover that the difference between an inmate and an officer is sometimes simply geography, because they're all prisoners in surprisingly different ways. Like the original Prisoner Cell Block H, Wentworth Prison is, at its heart, a series about survival, a character drama featuring women living in a pressure cooker environment. Despite the rivalries and power struggles, this family of misfits and rebels are forced to forge unlikely friendships and allegiances if they want to survive their time inside.</p>","updated":1602252281,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1828"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1872555"}}},{"id":1829,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1829/psychic-matchmaker","name":"Psychic Matchmaker","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Running","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-05-01","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"22:30","days":[]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":80,"name":"TLC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":43681,"thetvdb":295295,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/302/755209.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/302/755209.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Love is all about finding the perfect connection, and according to psychic Deborah Graham, that connection is a subconscious link that lives inside a person's soul. Deborah is an expert at discovering that bond, and she specializes in helping people find true love that can last a lifetime. Follow Deborah as she uses her psychic gift and an ever-growing \"date-a-base\" to find her clients their soulmate, even if it means searching in unlikely places to get the perfect lead.</p>","updated":1617534197,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1829"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/792363"}}},{"id":1830,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1830/the-willis-family","name":"The Willis Family","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Family","Music"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-05","officialSite":"http://www.tlc.com/tv-shows/the-willis-family/","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":80,"name":"TLC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48812,"thetvdb":295157,"imdb":"tt4634400"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/302/755284.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/302/755284.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>The Willis Family</b> is a new series following a musically gifted family of fourteen — 4 boys, 8 girls and parents Brenda and Toby — as they make music at home and on the road.</p>","updated":1617545476,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1830"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/655818"}}},{"id":1831,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1831/the-briefcase","name":"The Briefcase","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-27","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"20:00","days":["Wednesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":2,"name":"CBS","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48857,"thetvdb":295059,"imdb":"tt4658248"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/280/701988.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/280/701988.jpg"},"summary":"<p>The show features a social experiment element. In each episode, two hard-working American families experiencing financial setbacks are presented by the show's producers with a briefcase containing $101,000 and a potentially life-altering decision: they can keep all of the money for themselves, or give all or part of it to another family in need.</p>","updated":1605221234,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1831"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/181140"}}},{"id":1832,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1832/the-secret-war","name":"The Secret War","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":["War"],"status":"Ended","runtime":50,"premiered":"1977-01-05","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":8,"network":{"id":12,"name":"BBC One","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":null,"thetvdb":81910,"imdb":"tt2341725"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/10/26695.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26695.jpg"},"summary":"<p>The series traces the moves and countermoves between British and German scientists on land, sea, and in the air.</p>","updated":1613828153,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1832"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155503"}}},{"id":1833,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1833/banished","name":"Banished","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-03-05","officialSite":"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p02jfvpn","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":8.3},"weight":53,"network":{"id":37,"name":"BBC Two","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47763,"thetvdb":292323,"imdb":"tt3508050"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/80/201739.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/80/201739.jpg"},"summary":"<p>At its heart, <b>Banished</b> is a story of survival. Though it is set in the stark historical reality of the founding of the penal colony in Australia in 1788 after the arrival of the First Fleet, it is not the story of Australia and how it came to be. Rather, it is a tale of love, faith, justice and morality played out on an epic scale in a confined community where the stakes are literally life and death.</p>","updated":1577255062,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1833"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155510"}}},{"id":1834,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1834/1864","name":"1864","type":"Scripted","language":"Danish","genres":["Drama","War"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2014-10-12","officialSite":"http://www.dr.dk/diverse/drama/1864/index","schedule":{"time":"20:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":9},"weight":70,"network":{"id":115,"name":"DR1","country":{"name":"Denmark","code":"DK","timezone":"Europe/Copenhagen"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":45398,"thetvdb":286287,"imdb":"tt1753353"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/62/157336.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/62/157336.jpg"},"summary":"<p>When Germany and Prussia declare war on Denmark, two brothers are called to serve in the bloodiest battle in Denmark's history. We follow the brothers Peter and Laust during the years of the Second Schleswig War, two brothers in love with the same woman.</p>","updated":1616933726,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1834"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/155518"}}},{"id":1835,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1835/reno-rumble","name":"Reno Rumble","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["DIY"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-05","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"19:30","days":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":120,"name":"Nine Network","country":{"name":"Australia","code":"AU","timezone":"Australia/Sydney"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48833,"thetvdb":294726,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/10/26896.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26896.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Reno Rumble</b> is an Australian reality television series that pit former contestants from The Block on the Nine Network against former contestants from House Rules on the Seven Network.</p><p>Contestants renovate two suburban houses, with one team eliminated each week. The winner will receive a $100,000 cheque with half going to the winning couple's favourite charity. Each home will be judged by interior design experts who have been briefed by the home owners on the style they want for their renovation. The runner up will receive $50,000 with half going to charity</p><p>Each week, each home will be blind judged (unaware of which team renovated which one – or the rooms assigned to each individual couple) and the team with the lowest score that week will be eliminated from the competition.</p><p><i>Reno Rumble: East v West</i> is the second season of Australian reality television series <i>Reno Rumble</i>, it will air on the Nine Network. Unlike the first season which pit former contestants from <i>The Block</i> against former contestants from <i>House Rules</i>, this season will have state based rookie teams from either The East or West Side of Australia competing against each other. It will be hosted by Scott Cam and Shelley Craft and will be judged by Colin McAllister and Justin Ryan. It will premiere Monday 21 March 2016. The winning couple will receive $100,000.</p>","updated":1570905126,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1835"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/734925"}}},{"id":1836,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1836/the-block","name":"The Block","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Running","runtime":70,"premiered":"2003-06-01","officialSite":"https://9now.nine.com.au/the-block","schedule":{"time":"19:30","days":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.6},"weight":65,"network":{"id":120,"name":"Nine Network","country":{"name":"Australia","code":"AU","timezone":"Australia/Sydney"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":2185,"thetvdb":74768,"imdb":"tt0418372"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/10/26834.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26834.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>The Block </b>is an Australian reality television show. The show sees four couples compete against each other to renovate a home in an apartment block and sell it at auction for the highest price.</p>","updated":1606072019,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1836"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1970885"}}},{"id":1837,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1837/frontline","name":"Frontline","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":["Drama"],"status":"Running","runtime":90,"averageRuntime":63,"premiered":"1989-01-18","officialSite":"http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/frontline/","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday","Friday"]},"rating":{"average":8.6},"weight":94,"network":{"id":85,"name":"PBS","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":8258,"thetvdb":80646,"imdb":"tt0133302"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27545.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27545.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Since it began in 1983, <b>Frontline</b> has been airing public-affairs documentaries that explore a wide scope of the complex human experience. Frontline's goal is to extend the impact of the documentary beyond its initial broadcast by serving as a catalyst for change.</p><p>.</p>","updated":1620381049,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1837"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2078046"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2085360"}}},{"id":1838,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1838/sons-of-winter","name":"Sons of Winter","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-04-28","officialSite":"https://www.discovery.com/tv-shows/sons-of-winter/","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":66,"name":"Discovery Channel","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48404,"thetvdb":295071,"imdb":"tt4649582"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/302/755285.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/302/755285.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Meet the Barks family, homesteaders who have rejected modern living in favor of living off the grid and maintaining a prairie lifestyle in Northern Saskatchewan, a remote province in Canada. This winter, their entire world is about to change. The two eldest sons, 20-year-old Dale and 19-year-old Shane, will embark on an epic, 90-day journey hundreds of miles away from home in order to survive the unforgiving wilderness on their own.</p>","updated":1617545502,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1838"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/167404"}}},{"id":1839,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1839/monument-guys","name":"Monument Guys","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-06","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Wednesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":53,"name":"History","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48949,"thetvdb":295255,"imdb":"tt4493812"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27546.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27546.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Some people make history with their actions, and some people make it with molten bronze. At the Crucible Foundry in Norman Oklahoma, brothers Mark and Steve Palmerton, and sculptor Craig Campbell, research, sculpt, and cast bronze statues of deserving heroes—dead and alive, celebrated and forgotten. In small towns across America, these monuments ensure a legacy that will last for thousands of years, and the crew at the Crucible will go to any means to make sure they're done right.</p>","updated":1532845960,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1839"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/228335"}}},{"id":1840,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1840/lost-in-transmission","name":"Lost in Transmission","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-07","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":53,"name":"History","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48956,"thetvdb":294929,"imdb":"tt4569998"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27547.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27547.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Top Gear co-host and automotive aficionado, Rutledge Wood and his friend and fellow car fanatic, George Flanigen, are on a mission: to rescue America's greatest rides from barns and backyards across the South.</p><p>Together Rutledge and George will comb the garages of America to rescue the under-appreciated examples of automotive styling that time forgot, fix them up and get them back on the road. Their journey will take them off the beaten track, where they will get lost in local traditions, meet eccentric characters, and discover the heart of American car culture.</p><p>Two friends on the ultimate road trip saving America's greatest, weirdest and coolest cars.</p>","updated":1613904912,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1840"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157091"}}},{"id":1841,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1841/dead-end-express","name":"Dead End Express","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-07","officialSite":"http://channel.nationalgeographic.com/dead-end-express/","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":42,"name":"National Geographic Channel","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48808,"thetvdb":296098,"imdb":"tt4622766"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/296/741554.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/296/741554.jpg"},"summary":"<p>On the edge of the American frontier, a few brave men risk their lives delivering vital supplies to people living off the grid. From the dense woodlands of Montana's Flathead National Forest, through the isolated heart of Idaho's Hells Canyon, to the frozen wastelands of Alaska's high tundra, follow five rugged adventurers as they live and breath the high-stakes of hauling critical cargo into these unique tracts of wilderness. Always on the move, these deliverymen have been shaped by the great outdoors, and have learned the hard way how to tackle anything that Mother Nature throws in their path. Yet they all have one thing in common: there's no job too tough. And whether by bush plane, jet boat, snowmachine, dog-sled or pack horse, they'll overcome all obstacles and do whatever it takes to make their delivery.</p>","updated":1613269758,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1841"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/166072"}}},{"id":1842,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1842/the-island","name":"The Island","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Action","Adventure"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-05-25","officialSite":"http://nbc.com/the-island","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":6.8},"weight":0,"network":{"id":1,"name":"NBC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48933,"thetvdb":295583,"imdb":"tt4063608"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/26/67444.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/26/67444.jpg"},"summary":"<p>In the hour-long <b>The Island</b>, internationally acclaimed adventurer and survivalist Bear Grylls gives the modern American man the ultimate challenge: Can a man of today's world survive on a deserted island without the luxuries - or even the basics - of contemporary everyday life?</p><p>The Island, based on the hit Shine TV-produced Channel 4 U.K. series of the same name, doesn't include any of the usual reality show trappings. There are no prizes. No eliminations. No winner. No camera teams. The entire series is filmed by the men themselves. The six episodes will show 14 American men isolated on a deserted island with only the clothes on their backs and minimal survival tools, committed to filming every moment themselves.</p><p>These 21st-century American men, who are accustomed to roofs over their heads, restaurants and the benefits of technology, are stripped of all modern conveniences and catapulted back to the basics. They must hunt for food, source water, erect shelter, build community and try to survive using only their strength, determination and know-how. All of the men, including a stay-at-home dad, a trauma surgeon, a firefighter and a criminal defense attorney, have something to prove to themselves and each other. This experiment takes them to the very edge of human endurance. They will test their physical, mental and emotional limits and fight for their very existence.</p>","updated":1576915075,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1842"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/177894"}}},{"id":1843,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1843/golan-the-insatiable","name":"Golan the Insatiable","type":"Animation","language":"English","genres":["Comedy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":15,"premiered":"2013-11-23","officialSite":"http://www.fox.com/golan-the-insatiable/","schedule":{"time":"21:30","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":4,"name":"FOX","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":36254,"thetvdb":268652,"imdb":"tt3038384"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/10/26949.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26949.jpg"},"summary":"<p>I do not know how I got to your worthless dimension. I suspect foul wizardry. Nor do I know how to return to my kingdom of Gkruool. I do not like it any more than you insects. Yet here we are and it seems we must make the most of it.</p>","updated":1463043886,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1843"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/182286"}}},{"id":1844,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1844/stitchers","name":"Stitchers","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime","Science-Fiction"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-02","officialSite":"http://freeform.go.com/shows/stitchers","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":7.2},"weight":83,"network":{"id":26,"name":"FreeForm","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":42080,"thetvdb":292745,"imdb":"tt3868848"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/10/26950.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26950.jpg"},"summary":"<p>ABC Family's first procedural drama, <b>Stitchers</b>, follows Kirsten a young woman recruited into a covert government agency to be 'stitched' into the minds of the recently deceased, using their memories to investigate murders and decipher mysteries that otherwise would have gone to the grave. Working alongside Kirsten is Cameron, a brilliant neuroscientist whose passion for the program is evident in his work. The secret program is headed by Maggie, a skilled veteran of covert operations, and includes Linus, a socially immature bioelectrical engineer and communications technician. Kirsten's roommate, Camille, a gifted computer science grad student, is also recruited to use her skills to assist Kirsten in her new role as a \"stitcher\".</p>","updated":1573695902,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1844"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1231265"}}},{"id":1845,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1845/maron","name":"Maron","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Comedy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2013-05-03","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Wednesday"]},"rating":{"average":7.8},"weight":0,"network":{"id":65,"name":"IFC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":33285,"thetvdb":257993,"imdb":"tt2520512"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/31/77676.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/31/77676.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Marc Maron has been a comedian for 25 years. He's had his problems. He was an angry, drunk, self involved, twice divorced compulsive mess for most of his adult life, but with the popularity of a podcast he does in his garage and a life of sobriety, his life and career are turning around. <b>Maron </b>explores a fictionalized version of Marc's life, his relationships, and his career, including his incredibly popular WTF podcast, which features conversations Marc conducts with celebrities and fellow comedians. Neurosis intact, Maron is uniquely fascinating, absolutely compelling and brutally funny.</p>","updated":1615830848,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1845"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/790870"}}},{"id":1846,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1846/sexdrugsrockroll","name":"Sex&Drugs&Rock&Roll","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Comedy","Music"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-07-16","officialSite":"http://www.fxnetworks.com/shows/sex-drugs-rock-roll/episodes","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":6},"weight":53,"network":{"id":13,"name":"FX","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":39953,"thetvdb":283345,"imdb":"tt3594982"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/29/73112.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/29/73112.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Sex&amp;Drugs&amp;Rock&amp;Roll</b> follows Johnny Rock, lead singer of a legendary early 90s New York band called The Heathens. Known for living up to their name, the band partied so long and so hard that even Keith Richards thought they needed to slow things down. The Heathens were on the brink of becoming famous for their kickass live shows and the release of their highly anticipated first album. Until they broke up. The same day the album dropped. Because lead guitarist Flash found Johnny in bed with his wife. So the band became legendary for all the wrong reasons - like self-destructing sooner than any group in rock 'n' roll history. 25 years later the only thing bigger than Johnny's ego is his prostate. The drugs he really needs now aren't cocaine and marijuana - they're Crestor, Cymbalta and Cialis. He's out of work, out of money and out of show business options. That's when a massively talented young singer named Gigi shows up - with a burning desire to be famous, a throwback appreciation for The Heathens only album, and a stack of cash big enough to bring the whole band back into the studio. Only this time, she is the lead singer and Johnny is just a behind the scenes songwriter. The race is on to see who gets famous first - and for what reason.</p>",