it/11/27508.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27508.jpg"},"summary":"<p><i>The Muppets</i> return to prime time with a contemporary, documentary-style show that, for the first time ever, will explore the Muppets' personal lives and relationships, both at home and at work, as well as romances, break-ups, achievements, disappointments, wants and desires; a more adult Muppet show, for kids of all ages.</p>","updated":1574650126,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1866"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/618861"}}},{"id":1867,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1867/second-chance","name":"Second Chance","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime","Science-Fiction"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2016-01-13","officialSite":"http://www.fox.com/lookinglass","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Friday"]},"rating":{"average":7.7},"weight":76,"network":{"id":4,"name":"FOX","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":45795,"thetvdb":295684,"imdb":"tt4378456"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/159/397647.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/159/397647.jpg"},"summary":"<p>A thrilling new action-drama about a man brought back to life by two scientists playing god in the quest to save one of their own lives. Seventy-five-year-old Jimmy Pritchard is a shell of his former self. A drinker, a womanizer and a father who always put work before family, Pritchard was forced to resign as L.A. County Sheriff for corrupt conduct more than a decade ago. Now, some 15 unkind years later, he is killed when he stumbles upon a robbery at the home of FBI Agent Duval Pritchard, one of his two children. But death is surprisingly short for Jimmy, who is brought back to life by billionaire tech-genius twins Mary Goodwin and her brother, Otto, founders of the social networking empire, Lookinglass. Resurrected as a younger, better version of himself, with physical abilities of which he never dreamed, a re-animated Pritchard is given a <b>Second Chance</b> at life. What will he do with it? Will he try to repair the damage he did to his family? Will he embrace a new sense of purpose or fall prey to old temptations?</p>","updated":1580638818,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1867"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/635053"}}},{"id":1868,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1868/rosewood","name":"Rosewood","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime","Medical"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-09-23","officialSite":"http://www.fox.com/rosewood","schedule":{"time":"20:00","days":["Friday"]},"rating":{"average":7.3},"weight":8,"network":{"id":4,"name":"FOX","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47421,"thetvdb":295683,"imdb":"tt4465472"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/81/204177.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/81/204177.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Meet the Beethoven of private pathologists... From executive producer Todd Harthan, <b>Rosewood</b> is the story of Dr. Beaumont Rosewood, Jr., the most brilliant private pathologist in Miami. Using his wildly sophisticated autopsy lab, he performs for-hire autopsies to uncover clues that the Miami PD can't see. His new partner-in-crime is Detective Villa a Miami PD detective with attitude and demons to spare. While she's impressed by Rosewood's incredible abilities, his constant optimism is more annoying than it is infectious. But somehow, week-to-week, this unlikely tag team will solve many crimes together. Joining Rosewood in his practice are his sister and \"toxicology queen,\" Pippy; and DNA specialist Tara Milly Izikoff aka TMI, who is Pippy's fiancée. Plagued with his own set of medical ailments, Rosewood sees that every moment of life should be embraced and lived to the fullest. And those moments of victims' lives that will never be are what drive him the most.</p>","updated":1574012719,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1868"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096461"}}},{"id":1869,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1869/alone","name":"Alone","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Adventure"],"status":"To Be Determined","runtime":90,"averageRuntime":67,"premiered":"2015-06-18","officialSite":"http://www.history.com/shows/alone","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":8},"weight":97,"network":{"id":53,"name":"History","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48961,"thetvdb":295936,"imdb":"tt4803766"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/192/481495.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/192/481495.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Alone</b> places ten hardcore survivalists alone in the wilderness - no camera crew, no teams, no producers - on a single mission to stay alive. At stake is $500,000 awarded to the person who can last the longest. They will face extreme isolation and psychological distress as they plunge into the unknown, self-documenting their experience.</p>","updated":1621067288,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1869"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1902823"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2085334"}}},{"id":1870,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1870/leepu-pitbull","name":"Leepu & Pitbull","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-23","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":53,"name":"History","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48959,"thetvdb":296730,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/12/31425.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/12/31425.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Leepu &amp; Pitbull</b> follows master mechanic Pitbull Steve and renowned Bangladeshi car designer, who is named Leepu, as they transform heaps of metal into a cash-producing business venture. Each week a customer with a beloved clunker, great story and small budget asks this odd couple to convert their bucket of bolts into a cool custom car. In this high-risk and high-octane undertaking, it's up to Leepu &amp; Pitbull to turn their differences into inspiration... as they MacGuyver fixes to build winning wheels, satisfy the customer and rev up the riches.</p>","updated":1598793940,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1870"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/202701"}}},{"id":1871,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1871/mr-robot","name":"Mr. Robot","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime","Thriller"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-24","officialSite":"https://www.usanetwork.com/mr-robot","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":8.4},"weight":93,"network":{"id":30,"name":"USA Network","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":42422,"thetvdb":289590,"imdb":"tt4158110"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/211/528026.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/211/528026.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Mr. Robot</b> follows Elliot, a young programmer who works as a cyber-security engineer by day and as a vigilante hacker by night. Elliot finds himself at a crossroads when the mysterious leader of an underground hacker group recruits him to destroy the firm he is paid to protect. Compelled by his personal beliefs, Elliot struggles to resist the chance to take down the multinational CEOs he believes are running (and ruining) the world.</p>","updated":1613379939,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1871"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1762042"}}},{"id":1872,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1872/cold-justice-sex-crimes","name":"Cold Justice: Sex Crimes","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Crime"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-07-31","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Friday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":14,"name":"TNT","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48490,"thetvdb":298474,"imdb":"tt4661598"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/22/56927.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/22/56927.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Cold Justice: Sex Crimes</b> is an extremely timely project, especially in light of the sobering statistics for sex-related crimes in America revealing that there are approximately 240,000 survivors of sexual assault in America, including men, women and children. In fact, every two minutes, someone is sexually assaulted in the United States. To combat these numbers and bring justice to the survivors of sexual assault, former Harris County, Texas, prosecutors Casey Garrett and Alicia O'Neill are traveling to small towns around the country to help local law enforcement close cases that have sat dormant for years.</p>","updated":1590327984,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1872"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/190275"}}},{"id":1873,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1873/significant-mother","name":"Significant Mother","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Comedy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-08-03","officialSite":"https://www.cwtv.com/shows/significant-mother","schedule":{"time":"21:30","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":6.5},"weight":0,"network":{"id":5,"name":"The CW","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48614,"thetvdb":294477,"imdb":"tt3924978"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/84/210214.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/84/210214.jpg"},"summary":"<p>In <b>Significant Mother</b> budding Portland restaurateur Nate's world is turned upside down when he comes back from a business trip to find his lothario best friend and roommate, Jimmy, is now dating his recently separated mother, Lydia. To make matters worse, Nate's previously disinterested dad, Harrison is now determined to win Lydia back and isn't afraid to use Nate to get what he wants. Stuck between his family feud and his best friend's first serious relationship, Nate's \"new normal\" forever changes his relationships with his parents, and severely handicaps his own dating life.</p>","updated":1609034074,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1873"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/215361"}}},{"id":1874,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1874/mr-robinson","name":"Mr. Robinson","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Comedy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"averageRuntime":30,"premiered":"2015-08-05","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Wednesday"]},"rating":{"average":6},"weight":56,"network":{"id":1,"name":"NBC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":39916,"thetvdb":281592,"imdb":"tt2800234"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/12/31449.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/12/31449.jpg"},"summary":"<p>As lead singer and keyboardist of the funk band Nasty Delicious, Craig knows a thing or two about working the crowd, but his day job is where he really makes the grade. Every struggling artist knows the drill: You've got to pay the bills while you wait for that big break. So when Craig finds himself short on cash, he takes a job as a substitute high school music teacher. It's an easy gig, right? The school principal believes that rules were made to be strictly upheld. She's none too fond of Craig's unorthodox teaching style, or his crush on the pretty English teacher. It's a constant struggle for Craig, having one foot in the music world with his band, Nasty Delicious, and one foot in the teaching world. But if Craig wants to get the girl of his dreams and teach these kids the joys of music, he'll have to buckle down, shape up and get the funk out. <b>Mr. Robinson</b> is inspired by Robinson's real-life experiences as a music teacher.</p>","updated":1620061902,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1874"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157208"}}},{"id":1875,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1875/public-morals","name":"Public Morals","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Crime"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-08-25","officialSite":"http://www.tntdrama.com/shows/public-morals.html%20?sr=public_morals_tnt","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Tuesday"]},"rating":{"average":7.3},"weight":0,"network":{"id":14,"name":"TNT","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":38664,"thetvdb":281707,"imdb":"tt3597854"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/25/64060.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/25/64060.jpg"},"summary":"<p>This summer, TNT is going to take viewers to the seedy, gritty streets and the bright, seductive lights of 1960s New York with <b>Public Morals</b>, a powerful, buzz-generating police drama from writer, director, executive producer and star Edward Burns (Saving Private Ryan, The Brothers McMullen, TNT's Mob City). Public Morals also stars Michael Rapaport (Justified, Prison Break) and Elizabeth Masucci (The Americans, Inside Amy Schumer). The series centers on Terry Muldoon (Burns), an officer of the Public Morals Division, which investigates vice crimes in the city. Many of Muldoon's fellow cops in the division walk a thin line between morality and crime as vice-related temptations threaten to snare even the best of officers, including Muldoon's partner, Charlie Bullman (Rapoport). As Muldoon watches the Hells Kitchen streets where he grew up devoured by an escalating war within two factions of the Irish-American Mob, he becomes more determined than ever to fight back against the city's dark underbelly so he can provide a safe place where he and his wife, Christine (Masucci), can raise their family.</p>","updated":1611508281,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1875"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/215936"}}},{"id":1876,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1876/todrick","name":"Todrick","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-08-31","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"22:30","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":22,"name":"MTV","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48766,"thetvdb":296544,"imdb":"tt4635268"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/12/31513.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/12/31513.jpg"},"summary":"<p>In his new weekly MTV docu-series, quadruple-threat Todrick Hall lets fans into his creative factory and introduces them to the passionate troupe of creative collaborators who pour heart and soul into his weekly videos.</p>","updated":1466908452,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1876"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/215365"}}},{"id":1877,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1877/girl-code-live","name":"Girl Code Live","type":"Talk Show","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Running","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-08-31","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"22:30","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":22,"name":"MTV","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48767,"thetvdb":299870,"imdb":"tt4953380"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/16/40913.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/16/40913.jpg"},"summary":"<p><i><b>\"Girl Code Live\"</b></i> is a weekly half-hour late night talk show hosted by three hilarious ladies from \"Girl Code\" - Nessa, Carly and Awkwafina. The series will feature celebrity guests, musical artists, fun games and candid girl-talk in front of a live studio audience.</p>","updated":1575308295,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1877"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/395632"}}},{"id":1878,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1878/thunderbirds-are-go","name":"Thunderbirds Are Go","type":"Animation","language":"English","genres":["Action","Adventure","Science-Fiction"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2015-04-04","officialSite":"http://www.thunderbirds.com/","schedule":{"time":"08:30","days":["Saturday"]},"rating":{"average":7.8},"weight":81,"network":{"id":35,"name":"ITV","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":38148,"thetvdb":266631,"imdb":"tt3138604"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/250/627103.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/250/627103.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Thunderbirds Are Go</b> is a remake of the hit 1960's television show. In the 21st century, Jeff Tracy, a former astronaut, amasses a colossal fortune and decides that he must use it to benefit others. His answer to this desire is to create International Rescue, a unique private emergency response service equipped with customized designed vehicles and equipment that enable the organization to react to any crisis whether it be in sea, air, land, or space. Jeff's five sons volunteer to operate as the pilots and field agents, as well \"Brain\" who acts as the teams engineer. In addition, Jeff's friend, Kyrano and his daughter Tanusha aka Kayo (based on the original series Tin-Tin character) agree to be the support staff. In addition to the field team, IR also maintains an intelligence network with Lady Penelope and her ex-con chauffeur, Parker as the chief agents in this arm. The series depicts this team as they answer various calls for help around and beyond the world while they prevent enemies like the Hood from learning and exploiting their secrets.</p>","updated":1610184940,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1878"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1799787"}}},{"id":1879,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1879/femme-fatales","name":"Femme Fatales","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Crime","Thriller"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2011-05-13","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"23:00","days":["Friday"]},"r