11/27586.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Experts and a lively audience join Dara O Briain to tackle the biggest concepts in science and discover the great ideas that are changing the world we live in.</p>","updated":1608085825,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1883"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157450"}}},{"id":1884,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1884/wild-palms","name":"Wild Palms","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Science-Fiction","Thriller"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"1993-05-16","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"00:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7},"weight":44,"network":{"id":3,"name":"ABC","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":324,"thetvdb":76174,"imdb":"tt0106175"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27587.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27587.jpg"},"summary":"<p>A dark, sexy, noir Los Angeles of the future is the backdrop for Oliver Stone's haunting, sci-fi saga of greed, treason and virtual reality. Harry Wyckoff is about to become a player in a dark and terrifying battle where everything is at stake and no one is who they seem. Featuring an all-star cast, this story about a cult, a corporation, and a conspiracy to rule the country, is one of the most original movie events in recent history.</p>","updated":1599716436,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1884"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157455"}}},{"id":1885,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1885/vip","name":"V.I.P.","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Comedy","Action","Crime"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"averageRuntime":60,"premiered":"1998-09-26","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"","days":["Saturday"]},"rating":{"average":7},"weight":8,"network":{"id":72,"name":"Syndication","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":6494,"thetvdb":74181,"imdb":"tt0134269"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27588.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27588.jpg"},"summary":"<p>A campy syndicated series about Vallery Irons, a girl working at a hot-dog stand who accidentally saves a celebrity and is mistaken for a bodyguard. She and a team of beautiful bodyguards form a bodyguard agency called V.I.P. which stands for Vallery Irons Protection. When Vallery Irons first comes to California, she has no idea that her big break will come from a date with a famous action star. While attending a Hollywood premiere, a crazed fan pulls a gun - but her movie hunk turns into a coward, and it's Vallery who becomes the hero. Suddenly, she's thrown into a world of action and danger as owner of a Hollywood protection agency (V.I.P. or Vallery Irons Protection), taking the risks to protect others at a price few are willing to pay.</p>","updated":1620064817,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1885"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157543"}}},{"id":1886,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1886/sweating-bullets","name":"Sweating Bullets","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Action","Crime"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"1991-04-08","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"23:30","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":7},"weight":8,"network":{"id":2,"name":"CBS","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":5427,"thetvdb":74988,"imdb":"tt0101226"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27593.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27593.jpg"},"summary":"<p>After an unconventional DEA cop gets fired, he begins a new job as a private investigator in Florida. Feeling at first like he was in paradise, it wasn't long before his eyes were opened to both the ugliness of the crimes and the beauty of the women.</p>","updated":1610531871,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1886"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157609"}}},{"id":1887,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1887/this-is-england","name":"This is England","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Drama"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2010-09-07","officialSite":"http://www.channel4.com/programmes/this-is-england-90","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":8},"weight":8,"network":{"id":45,"name":"Channel 4","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":26481,"thetvdb":187351,"imdb":"tt1685471"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27594.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27594.jpg"},"summary":"<p>The first two series of the Channel 4 drama written and directed by Shane Meadows revisiting the characters from his 2007 film <b>This is England</b>. In This is England '86 Thomas Turgoose reprises his role as Shaun, a school-leaver with few prospects in mid-1980s England. Shaun and his friends must attempt to deal with the issues posed by the transition to adulthood in an unstable social climate where 3.4 million people are unemployed and there are strikes, race riots and anti-nuclear protests. The events of This is England '88 take place two years on from the initial spin-off series. Set in and around Christmas, there is a distinct absence of festive spirit as Lol (Vicky McClure) and Woody (Joe Gilgun) struggle to come to terms with events from the past. Shaun, meanwhile, learns first-hand the pain that love can bring.</p>","updated":1577690224,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1887"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/317614"}}},{"id":1888,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1888/the-team","name":"The Team","type":"Scripted","language":"German","genres":["Drama","Crime","Thriller"],"status":"To Be Determined","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-02-28","officialSite":"http://theteam.zdfe-b2b.de","schedule":{"time":"","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.8},"weight":70,"network":{"id":115,"name":"DR1","country":{"name":"Denmark","code":"DK","timezone":"Europe/Copenhagen"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47770,"thetvdb":291265,"imdb":"tt3681610"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/164/411992.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/164/411992.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Criminals don't stop at borders, and neither should the police. <b>The Team</b> portrays a group of European police officers fighting international crime throughout Europe. The series is written by specialists Peter Thorsboe and Mai Brostrøm (The Eagle, The Protectors) – names that guarantee well-grounded and vividly inventive cases with complex, stimulating characters.</p><p><i>The Team</i> consists of forensics, legal and IT experts, along with profilers and psychologists; their cases take them to Europe's major cities. The series benefits from Europe's huge cultural diversity and is shot in original languages. It sheds light into the reality of today's organized crime, as well as into the fates behind the crimes. <i>The Team</i> sees to it that justice wins and the victims' dignity is restored.</p>","updated":1586910715,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1888"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1515335"}}},{"id":1889,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1889/taken","name":"Taken","type":"Scripted","language":"English","genres":["Science-Fiction"],"status":"Ended","runtime":90,"premiered":"2002-12-02","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"20:00","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":8.3},"weight":8,"network":{"id":16,"name":"Syfy","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":5447,"thetvdb":78224,"imdb":"tt0289830"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27603.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27603.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Covering a period from 1947 to the present, <b>Taken </b>focused on three different families, each of whom was profoundly affected by extraterrestrial visitation. The Keys family was headed by WWII bomber pilot Russell Keys, who spent virtually his entire adult life haunted by his \"close encounter\" with aliens. The Clarkes were originally represented by lonely Texas waitress Sally Clarke, who was impregnated by a charming stranger (John) who turned out to be an alien survivor of the Roswell crash. And the lives of the Crawfords were dictated by ruthless Army officer Owen Crawford, who was determined to prove that the government had covered up the truth about Roswell by dedicating his life to tracking down all space aliens and their half-human descendants. The story was narrated by Allie Keys, a \"hybrid\" child of the present day, whose story determined the outcome of the final episodes.</p>","updated":1536277614,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1889"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/157634"}}},{"id":1890,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1890/stripperella","name":"Stripperella","type":"Animation","language":"English","genres":["Action"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2003-06-26","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"23:00","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":7.4},"weight":8,"network":{"id":34,"na