Mortal Kombat: Defenders of the Realm","type":"Animation","language":"English","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"1996-09-21","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"","days":["Saturday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":30,"name":"USA Network","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":4530,"thetvdb":73711,"imdb":"tt0122355"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27813.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27813.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Mortal Kombat: Defenders of the Realm</b> is an animated series based on the popula Mortal Kombat fighting game franchise.</p>","updated":1609026857,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1937"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/159839"}}},{"id":1938,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1938/serial-experiments-lain","name":"Serial Experiments Lain","type":"Animation","language":"Japanese","genres":["Anime","Science-Fiction","Thriller"],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"1998-07-06","officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":8.6},"weight":54,"network":{"id":76,"name":"TV Tokyo","country":{"name":"Japan","code":"JP","timezone":"Asia/Tokyo"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":12408,"thetvdb":78814,"imdb":"tt0500092"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27814.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27814.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Close the World. Open the Next. Decades before the internet was something people carried around in their pockets, these words introduced anime fans to a surreal existence where computer monitors served as portals to brave new worlds. Serial Experiments: Lain and its deceptively \"ordinary\" title character redefined an entire generation's concept of the world wide web, prompting us all to suspiciously take note of humming power lines and central processing units. Follow along as fourteen year old Lain – driven by the abrupt suicide of a classmate – logs on to the Wired and promptly loses herself in a twisted mass of hallucinations, memories, and interconnected-psyches. Close the World. Open the Next. It's as simple as the flip of a switch.</p>","updated":1569845342,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1938"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/159852"}}},{"id":1939,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1939/psycho-pass","name":"Psycho-Pass","type":"Animation","language":"Japanese","genres":["Action","Anime","Crime","Science-Fiction"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2012-10-12","officialSite":"http://psycho-pass.com","schedule":{"time":"00:55","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":8.1},"weight":65,"network":{"id":131,"name":"Fuji TV","country":{"name":"Japan","code":"JP","timezone":"Asia/Tokyo"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":32925,"thetvdb":262090,"imdb":"tt2379308"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27816.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27816.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Welcome to a world where just thinking about a crime is enough to enough to make you guilty. Bad intentions can no longer be hidden, and the police know exactly which tainted minds are about to cross over to the wrong side of the law. The great equalizer in the war on thugs is the Dominator, a futuristic weapon that can read minds and assess the risk that a citizen will turn criminal. Cops work in teams made up of Enforcers and Inspectors. Enforcers take out the bad guys, Inspectors stop their partners from going rogue, and the all-powerful Sibyl System keeps a watchful eye on us all. Society is paralyzed by its deepest, darkest desires, and trial by jury has been replaced by the wrath of the Dominator. Welcome to the future. How guilty are you?</p>","updated":1604752712,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1939"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1723031"}}},{"id":1940,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1940/kekkai-sensen","name":"Kekkai Sensen","type":"Animation","language":"Japanese","genres":["Action","Anime","Fantasy","Supernatural"],"status":"Ended","runtime":25,"premiered":"2015-04-05","officialSite":"http://kekkaisensen.com/","schedule":{"time":"03:08","days":["Saturday"]},"rating":{"average":7.4},"weight":0,"network":{"id":24,"name":"MBS","country":{"name":"Japan","code":"JP","timezone":"Asia/Tokyo"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":48051,"thetvdb":289886,"imdb":"tt4379632"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/130/326154.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/130/326154.jpg"},"summary":"<p>A breach between Earth and the netherworlds has opened up over the city of New York, trapping New Yorkers and creatures from other dimensions in an impenetrable bubble. They've lived together for years, in a world of crazy crime sci-fi sensibilities. Now someone is threatening to sever the bubble, and a group of stylish superhumans is working to keep it from happening.</p>","updated":1568119194,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1940"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1360222"}}},{"id":1942,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1942/junketsu-no-maria","name":"Junketsu No Maria","type":"Animation","language":"Japanese","genres":["Comedy","Anime","Fantasy"],"status":"Ended","runtime":25,"premiered":"2015-01-11","officialSite":"http://junketsu-maria.tv/","schedule":{"time":"22:30","days":["Saturday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":132,"name":"Tokyo MX","country":{"name":"Japan","code":"JP","timezone":"Asia/Tokyo"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47117,"thetvdb":286856,"imdb":"tt4219154"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27818.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/11/27818.jpg"},"summary":"<p>In the midst of the Hundred Years' War lives teenage witch Maria. Hating war in all its forms, Maria interferes in battle after battle—ensuring no victory on either side. But when the heavens themselves have had enough of Maria's meddling, the angels decree that she may no longer use magic in public; and should she ever lose her virginity, she will lose her magic powers completely.</p>","updated":1503781075,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1942"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/159910"}}},{"id":1943,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1943/saenai-heroine-no-sodatekata","name":"Saenai Heroine no Sodatekata","type":"Animation","language":"Japanese","genres":["Comedy","Anime","Romance"],"status":"Ended","runtime":25,"premiered":"2015-01-15","officialSite":"http://www.saenai.tv/","schedule":{"time":"00:55","days":["Thursday"]},"rating":{"average":5.5},"weight":0,"network":{"id":131,"name":"Fuji TV","country":{"name":"Japan","code":"JP","timezone":"Asia/Tokyo"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":47109,"thetvdb":281275,"imdb":"tt3612626"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/117/294352.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/117/294352.jpg"},"summary":"<p>One day on his way home, hardcore otaku Tomoya encounters a beautiful girl in a scene seemingly torn directly out of a dating simulation game. Inspired, he decides to create his own dating sim based around this girl. There is just one problem: In reality the girl, Megumi, is normal and rather boring—nothing like the heroine of his imagination.</p>","