men to test their bodies and brains in three ultimate challenges that ask nothing more than for them to hit the Bullseye - literally. Comedian Godfrey (\"The Godfrey Complex\") will serve as co-host. Bullseye's fierce \"weekend warriors\" will participate in three levels of extraordinary challenges, all of which involve using their bodies like human darts to hit targets - on land, sea and air. As the rounds advance in this fun-for-the-family summer series, only those with the sharpest aim move forward. The first challenge finds the eight competitors vying to hit the center of a stationary target while leaping from a moving 18-wheeler, being pulled by a helicopter or acting as a human slingshot being projected hundreds of feet through the air. In round two, the remaining four competitors - two men and two women - race to hit as many targets as possible. These competitors may be aiming for targets while descending down a building or jumping between two racing speedboats. In the third and final challenge, the remaining three competitors race against the clock to conquer the ultimate test and hit the final Bullseye.</p>","updated":1613758734,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1968"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/182285"}}},{"id":1969,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1969/becoming-us","name":"Becoming Us","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Drama","Family"],"status":"Ended","runtime":60,"premiered":"2015-06-08","officialSite":"http://abcfamily.go.com/shows/becoming-us/video/latest/VDKA0_04joe00n","schedule":{"time":"22:00","days":["Monday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":26,"name":"FreeForm","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":49207,"thetvdb":294716,"imdb":"tt4604692"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/11/27922.jpg","original":"https://static.tv